' Auteur: DCCS
' ST Magazine nø28.
' GfA Basic 2 & 3, haute r‚solution.
'
Graphmode 3
Setcolor 0,0
Hidem
While Inkey$=""
  X=Int(Rnd*300)+100
  Y=Int(Rnd*200)+100
  For I=0 To 639
    Line X,Y,I,0
    Line X,Y,639-I,399
  Next I
  For I=0 To 399
    Line X,Y,639,I
    Line X,Y,0,399-I
  Next I
  Pause 80
  Cls
Wend
Showm
Setcolor 0,1
